    "updated_at": "2013-08-05T08:59:23Z",
    "body": "I close this PR since there is no essential reason to have this option, at least for now.\nDevelopers could do `RUSTFLAGS='--cfg unicode ...' make ...`, so, in its experimental stage, we don't lose anything not to have this option.\n\nThank you for your clarification, @graydon.\n",
